  <summary date="2021-07-16T12:38:21Z" status="Introduced in House">Middle Class Savings Act

 This bill modifies the tax brackets that apply to taxes on capital gains. The bill aligns the thresholds with the brackets for the regular income tax rates enacted in P.L. 115-97 (commonly known as the Tax Cuts and Jobs Act).</summary>
